OL,3,CHarvard removes human skin from
OL,4,Cbinding of 19th century book
OL,6,FIt said "a book about the human soul
OL,7,Fdeserved to have a human covering,"
OL,8,Fassociate university librarian Thomas
OL,9,FHyry said in a published question-and-
OL,10,Fanswer segment online Wednesday.
OL,12,FThe note also detailed the process
OL,13,Fbehind preparing the skin for binding.
OL,15,FScientific analysis done in 2014
OL,16,Fconfirmed the binding was made of
OL,17,Fhuman skin, the university said.
