OL,3,CHarvard removes human skin from
OL,4,Cbinding of 19th century book
OL,6,FIn a statement, Harvard said the
OL,7,Flibrary noted several ways in which
OL,8,Fits stewardship practices failed to
OL,9,Fmeet its ethical standards.
OL,11,F"Until relatively recently, the
OL,12,Flibrary has made the book available to
OL,13,Fanyone who asked for it, regardless of
OL,14,Ftheir reason for wishing to consult
OL,15,Fit," Harvard said.
