OL,3,CHarvard removes human skin from
OL,4,Cbinding of 19th century book
OL,6,FHarvard said the skin removal was
OL,7,Fprompted by a library review following
OL,8,Fa Harvard University report on human
OL,9,Fremains in its museum collections,
OL,10,Freleased in 2022.
OL,12,F"Harvard Library and the Harvard
OL,13,FMuseum Collections Returns Committee
OL,14,Fconcluded that the human remains used
OL,15,Fin the book's binding no longer belong
OL,16,Fin the Harvard Library collections,
OL,17,Fdue to the ethically fraught nature of
OL,18,Fthe book's origins and subsequent
OL,19,Fhistory," Harvard's statement said.
